      "span_text": "For studies involving EGFR inhibitor AG1478 (Calbiochem, EMD Biosciences Inc., La Jolla, CA), cells were pretreated with AG1478 (500 nM) for 30 min as previously described, and seeded in serum-free RPMI with or without Kp-10 (10 nM) in addition to AG1478 (500 nM) or vehicle control (DMSO)"
